{"id":96,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":96,"title":"Acts 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","The Acts",["br"],"of the Apostles"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus ministers for forty days after His resurrection—The kingdom is to be restored to Israel at a later time—The Twelve are to bear witness in Jerusalem, Judæa, Samaria, and the uttermost parts of the earth—Jesus ascends into heaven—Matthias is chosen to fill the vacancy in the Twelve."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.1","order":"03.07.001.11798"},["b","1"],"The former treatise have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"I"],"made, O",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Theophilus"],", of all that Jesus began both to do and teach,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.2","order":"03.07.001.11799"},["b","2"],"Until the day in which he was taken up, after that he through the Holy Ghost had given",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"commandments"],"unto the apostles whom he had chosen:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.3","order":"03.07.001.11800"},["b","3"],"To whom also he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"shewed"],"himself alive after his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"passion"],"by many infallible proofs, being seen of them forty days, and speaking of the things",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"pertaining"],"to the kingdom of God:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.4","order":"03.07.001.11801"},["b","4"],"And, being assembled together with",["i","them,"],"commanded them that they should not depart from Jerusalem, but wait for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"promise"],"of the Father, which,",["i","saith he,"],"ye have heard of me."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.5","order":"03.07.001.11802"},["b","5"],"For John truly baptized with water; but ye shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"baptized"],"with the Holy Ghost not many days hence."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.6","order":"03.07.001.11803"},["b","6"],"When they therefore were come together, they asked of him, saying, Lord, wilt thou at this time",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"restore"],"again the kingdom to Israel?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.7","order":"03.07.001.11804"},["b","7"],"And he said unto them, It is not for you to know the times or the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"seasons"],", which the Father hath put in his own power."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.8","order":"03.07.001.11805"},["b","8"],"But ye shall receive",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"power"],", after that the Holy Ghost is come upon you: and ye shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"witnesses"],"unto me both in Jerusalem, and in all Judæa, and in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"Samaria"],", and unto the uttermost part of the earth."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.9","order":"03.07.001.11806"},["b","9"],"And when he had spoken these things, while they beheld, he was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"taken"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"up"],"; and a cloud received him out of their sight."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.10","order":"03.07.001.11807"},["b","10"],"And while they looked steadfastly toward heaven as he went up, behold, two men stood by them in white apparel;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.11","order":"03.07.001.11808"},["b","11"],"Which also said, Ye men of Galilee, why stand ye gazing up into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"heaven"],"? this same Jesus, which is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"taken"],"up from you into heaven, shall so",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"come"],"in like",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"manner"],"as ye have seen him go into heaven."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.12","order":"03.07.001.11809"},["b","12"],"Then returned they unto Jerusalem from the mount called Olivet, which is from Jerusalem a sabbath day’s journey."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.13","order":"03.07.001.11810"},["b","13"],"And when they were come in, they went up into an upper room, where abode both Peter, and James, and John, and Andrew, Philip, and Thomas, Bartholomew, and Matthew, James",["i","the son"],"of Alphæus, and Simon Zelotes, and Judas",["i","the brother"],"of James."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.14","order":"03.07.001.11811"},["b","14"],"These all continued with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"one"],"accord in prayer and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"supplication"],", with the women, and Mary the mother of Jesus, and with his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"brethren"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.15","order":"03.07.001.11812"},["b","15"],"¶And in those days Peter stood up in the midst of the disciples, and said, (the number of names together were about an hundred and twenty,)"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.16","order":"03.07.001.11813"},["b","16"],"Men",["i","and"],"brethren, this scripture must needs have been fulfilled, which the Holy Ghost by the mouth of David",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"spake"],"before concerning",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"Judas"],", which was guide to them that took Jesus."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.17","order":"03.07.001.11814"},["b","17"],"For he was numbered with us, and had obtained part of this ministry."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.18","order":"03.07.001.11815"},["b","18"],"Now this man purchased a field with the reward of iniquity; and falling headlong, he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"burst"],"asunder in the midst, and all his bowels gushed out."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.19","order":"03.07.001.11816"},["b","19"],"And it was known unto all the dwellers at Jerusalem; insomuch as that field is called in their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"proper"],"tongue, Aceldama, that is to say, The field of blood."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.20","order":"03.07.001.11817"},["b","20"],"For it is written in the book of Psalms, Let his habitation be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"desolate"],", and let no man dwell therein: and his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"bishoprick"],"let another take."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.21","order":"03.07.001.11818"},["b","21"],"Wherefore of these men which have companied with us all the time that the Lord Jesus went in and out among us,"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.22","order":"03.07.001.11819"},["b","22"],"Beginning from the baptism of John, unto that same day that he was taken up from us, must one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"be"],"ordained to be a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"witness"],"with us of his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.23","order":"03.07.001.11820"},["b","23"],"And they appointed two, Joseph called Barsabas, who was surnamed Justus, and Matthias."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.24","order":"03.07.001.11821"},["b","24"],"And they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"prayed"],", and said, Thou, Lord, which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"knowest"],"the hearts of all",["i","men,"],"shew",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"whether"],"of these two thou hast",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_24d"},"chosen"],","],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.25","order":"03.07.001.11822"},["b","25"],"That he may take part of this ministry and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"apostleship"],", from which Judas by transgression",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"fell"],", that he might go to his own place."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.26","order":"03.07.001.11823"},["b","26"],"And they gave forth their lots; and the lot fell upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Matthias"],"; and he was numbered with the eleven apostles."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.1a","order":"03.07.001.11824"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/4.11.10-11"},"2 Tim. 4:11 (10–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.1b","order":"03.07.001.11826"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.3"},"Luke 1:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.2a","order":"03.07.001.11828"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.3a","order":"03.07.001.11830"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-postmortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Postmortal"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"},"Jesus Christ, Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.3b","order":"03.07.001.11832"},["b","3b"],["span.small","GR"],"suffering.",["span.small","JST"],"Acts 1:3 …",["i","sufferings"],"…"],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.3c","order":"03.07.001.11834"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.11"},"D&C 100:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.4a","order":"03.07.001.11836"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.9.8-10"},"D&C 95:9 (8–10)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promise"},"TG Promise"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.5a","order":"03.07.001.11838"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-baptism-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Baptism of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gift-of"},"Holy Ghost, Gift of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.6a","order":"03.07.001.11840"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dispensations"},"TG Dispensations"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.7a","order":"03.07.001.11842"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/2.21.19-22,28"},"Dan. 2:21 (19–22, 28)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/68.11.7-12"},"D&C 68:11 (7–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.12.12,27,31"},"121:12 (12, 27, 31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.8a","order":"03.07.001.11844"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/1.7"},"2 Tim. 1:7"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.8b","order":"03.07.001.11846"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/24.48"},"Luke 24:48"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.12"},"D&C 27:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.8c","order":"03.07.001.11848"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/8.5.5,14"},"Acts 8:5 (5, 14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.9a","order":"03.07.001.11850"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/10.18.18-19"},"3 Ne. 10:18 (18–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.8.8-10"},"11:8 (8–10)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"},"TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.9b","order":"03.07.001.11852"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/68.18"},"Ps. 68:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/4.8"},"Eph. 4:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.11a","order":"03.07.001.11854"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.10"},"1 Thes. 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.11b","order":"03.07.001.11856"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-ascension-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Ascension of"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.11c","order":"03.07.001.11858"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/14.3.1-4"},"John 14:3 (1–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.11d","order":"03.07.001.11860"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.14a","order":"03.07.001.11862"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"TG Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.14b","order":"03.07.001.11864"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.5.1-5"},"Moro. 6:5 (1–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.14c","order":"03.07.001.11866"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-family-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Family of"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.16a","order":"03.07.001.11868"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.16b","order":"03.07.001.11870"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/41.9"},"Ps. 41:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/22.48.47-48"},"Luke 22:48 (47–48)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.18a","order":"03.07.001.11872"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/27.5.3-10"},"Matt. 27:5 (3–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.19a","order":"03.07.001.11874"},["b","19a"],["span.small","GR"],"own."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.20a","order":"03.07.001.11876"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.25"},"Ps. 69:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.20b","order":"03.07.001.11878"},["b","20b"],["span.small","GR"],"overseership, office.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.8"},"Ps. 109:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/114.2"},"D&C 114:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.22a","order":"03.07.001.11880"},["b","22a"],["span.small","GR"],"become a witness."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.22b","order":"03.07.001.11882"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"TG Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.22c","order":"03.07.001.11884"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.24a","order":"03.07.001.11886"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/9.8.7-9"},"D&C 9:8 (7–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.24b","order":"03.07.001.11888"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.24c","order":"03.07.001.11890"},["b","24c"],["span.small","GR"],"which one."],["div",{"id":"24d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.24d","order":"03.07.001.11892"},["b","24d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.25a","order":"03.07.001.11894"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.25b","order":"03.07.001.11896"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/10.12"},"1 Cor. 10:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.9"},"D&C 3:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.26a","order":"03.07.001.11898"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostles"},"TG Apostles"],"."]]}
